  "body": "<p>I've been in the studio since March and have been wanting to film a studio tour ever since. You may remember the <a href=\"https://youtu.be/sZfjgkog1bY\">moving video</a>. Well I told myself once I got settled and got it all organized, I would do it. Instead I realized that I need to stop making excuses and just show the world how it actually looks most of the time. Please no judgements on the chaos. It is a working and functioning studio, even though there are still piles and bins that haven't been unpacked. Almost done editing the video, which will be done next week. For now, here is a sneak peek. Photography by <a href=\"http://annmarieloves.com/\">Ann-Marie Espinoza</a>. </p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1595890009110-ZYQJZRDHJPIK9W05OPE2/2a-New%2BStudio%2B_%2BAmy%2BTangerine.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n</figure>\n\n\n\n\n\n<img alt=\"2b-New+Studio+_+Amy+Tangerine.jpeg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1595890171474-61PLYLOX7NKSN3H5BWDE/2b-New%2BStudio%2B_%2BAmy%2BTangerine.jpeg\">\n</img>\n\n<img alt=\"2c-New+Studio+_+Amy+Tangerine.jpeg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1595890047835-LYIGF1KUF1732L41GLG8/2c-New%2BStudio%2B_%2BAmy%2BTangerine.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"2d-New+Studio+_+Amy+Tangerine.jpeg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1595890048744-JN89UQXWT6WPNK62N05M/2d-New%2BStudio%2B_%2BAmy%2BTangerine.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"2e-New+Studio+_+Amy+Tangerine.jpeg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1595890092856-4I9PQ6WTVKTMC5MWS2KY/2e-New%2BStudio%2B_%2BAmy%2BTangerine.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"2g-New+Studio+_+Amy+Tangerine.jpeg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1595890110309-7WJKYVI8FXSAIPW2K2U8/2g-New%2BStudio%2B_%2BAmy%2BTangerine.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"2f-New+Studio+_+Amy+Tangerine.jpeg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1595890093076-DB972NUCFWP2SLMO4KCB/2f-New%2BStudio%2B_%2BAmy%2BTangerine.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"2h-New+Studio+_+Amy+Tangerine.jpeg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1595890110365-J46FCS01A85L2Y15QFLM/2h-New%2BStudio%2B_%2BAmy%2BTangerine.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"2i-New+Studio+_+Amy+Tangerine.jpeg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1595890135201-29LEI3ZBS79YJ9UT3S7D/2i-New%2BStudio%2B_%2BAmy%2BTangerine.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"2j-New+Studio+_+Amy+Tangerine.jpeg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1595890135940-LQSKLPFWGUKYSQZWOBI9/2j-New%2BStudio%2B_%2BAmy%2BTangerine.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"2k-New+Studio+_+Amy+Tangerine.jpeg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1595890149836-7XKFKQ4XNYC64PYK36RA/2k-New%2BStudio%2B_%2BAmy%2BTangerine.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n\n\n<p>Come back by tomorrow at 9am for some really exciting news! </p>"
